@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vwsveo(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.80) / v1) - wp.abs(v1))
    v0 = 0.57
    v2 = ((0.02 + (v0 + 0.85 - v1 + 0.08)) * ((tmp + 0.93 / v1 + 0.08) + 0.32))
    v2 = wp.abs(wp.cos(v1))
    v1 = (wp.sin(0.49) + wp.sin(v2))
    v1 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.24) + (v0 + 0.54 - tmp + 0.11)) / wp.abs((v1 + 0.77 - tmp + 0.08)))
    data[tid] = v0
